Muslim Pro now comes with with Qalbox, a streaming service where you can stream Muslim-focused films, TV series and more.

Main Features:

• Accurate prayer times for salah based on your current location.
• Athan / Azan - visual and audio notifications for the call to prayer with global muezzin voices to choose from including Mishary Rashid Al-Afasy and Abdul Basit Abdus Samat.
• The Holy Quran (Al Qur'an) with audio recitations, phonetics and translations, colored Tajweed and more.
• Qibla compass and map to show you the direction to Makkah
• NEW! Hundreds of hours of curated Muslim-focused content on Qalbox - from films, TV series, kids' programmes, documentaries, and more.
• Fasting times (Imsak and Iftar) during Ramadan
• Tasbih for zikr
• Complete Muslim Hijri calendar with key Islamic events such as Eid-ul-Fitr, Eid-ul-Adha, and more.
• A library of inspiring content - from Muslim lifestyle articles to infographics on all things Muslim.
• Halal restaurants and mosques around you
• Hisn'ul Muslim: A collection of duas for daily needs
• Zakat calculator

The Muslim Pro app including the Qur'an is fully translated to: Bahasa Indonesia, Bahasa Melayu, Deutsch, English, Español, Français, Italiano, Nederlands, Português, Türkçe, العربية, اردو, русский, 简体中文, 日本語, ภาษาไทย


IMPORTANT:

If you find that the you are getting the wrong prayer times, please adjust your settings. In most cases, enabling auto-settings is the safest way to obtain the most accurate prayer times.
